<!doctype html>
<html lang="en" data-theme="dark">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://unpkg.com/@picocss/pico@1.*/css/pico.min.css" type="text/css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css"  type="text/css">
    <title>GoHang</title>
    <link rel="icon" href="data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22 viewBox=%220 0 100 100%22><text y=%22.9em%22 font-size=%2290%22>🫂</text></svg>" sizes="any" type="image/svg+xml">
    <script src="script.js"></script>
  </head>
  <body>
    <header class="container">
        <hgroup>
            <h1>🫂 GoHang</h1>
            <h2>Hang with the group chat (fr this time)</h2>
          </hgroup>
    </header>
    <main class="container">
        <article>
            <p>Find out the best time for an event/meetup and actually make it happen.</p>
            <form onsubmit="newEvent(); return false" class="grid">
                <input required type="text" name="eventName" id="eventName" placeholder="Event Name" max="128">
                <button id="eventButton">Make It Happen</button>
            </form>
        </article>
    </main>
    <footer class="container">
        <small>Made with ❤️ by <a href="https://www.buymeacoffee.com/yusufrahmn">Yusuf</a>, Zade, Mustafa, and Younes at <a href="https://devpost.com/software/gohang">uOttaHack 5</a>.</small>
    </footer>
  </body> 
</html>